A1  - Richter K.
A1  - Mach S.
A1  - Lisewski G.
Y1  - 1966//
N2  - Personal experience is related concerning 110 pneumopelvigrams performed for determination of the volume and site of the ovaries especially in the Stein-Leventhal syndrome and gonadal dysgenesis, the diagnosis of deformities, ovarian localization when the findings on palpation are indefinite, and the detection of recurrent tumors in the true pelvis. These conditions are considered to represent indications for urgent pneumopelvigraphy, The combination of conventional radiography with simultaneous tomography is a technically simple, safe and generally practicable examination, being a true extension of the accuracy of gynecologic diagnosis.
