T3  - Scndrome de Stein-Leventhal. a proposito de dos casos -
A1  - Sousa Santos R.
Y1  - 1962//
N2  - The author discusses the probable atiology of Stein-Leventhas syndrome and the pathogenesis. Two clinical cases are presented, treated by cuneiform resection of the ovaries. In one case the menstrual activity became normal. Two gestations with normal childbirth followed. In the other, more recently operated, menstruation became regular and it is hoped that the sterility will disappear.
