N2  - A case report of a 32-year-old housewife with Stein-Leventhal's syndrome is presented. As major signs, sterility and hypertrichosis, secondary amenorrhoea, hypoplasia of the uterus and clitoris, were noted. The function of the adrenal cortex was normal. A review of the literature, especially with regard to pathogenesis, symptomatology and differential diagnosis of this syndrome is given.
