T3  - Die laparoscopie in der gynakologie
A1  - Jaeger J.
A1  - Druner W.
Y1  - 1960//
N2  - Thanks to the further development of instruments during the course of the past few years, laparoscopy plays an ever increasing role in gynecological diagnosis today. Indications of special preference are sterility and extrauterine pregnancy. It contributes less often to lower abdominal tumors, endometriosis, Stein Leventhal syndrome and chronic inflammation. With careful technique compbcstions seldom arise.
