T1  - Study and treatment of the monophasic cycle
T3  - Estudio y tratamiento del ciclo monofasico
A1  - Silberman C.J.
A1  - Sobrero A.J.
Y1  - 1958//
N2  - If study of the basal metabolism, determination of the cholesterolaemia, determination of the I<ovid:sup>131</ovid:sup>, captation, the glucose tolerance curve and determination of the protein-bound iodine demonstrate dysfunction of the thyroid glands adequate treatment should be carried out: If the monophasic cycle is of adrenal origin (adrenogenital syndrome), treatment should be carried out with adrenal corticoids which, by acting on the hypophysis, diminish the ACTH production (cortisone, hydrooortisone, prednisoneorprednisolone, indosesof 12.5 mg., 10 mg., 2.5 mg., 2.5 mg., respectively, in all cases 3 times daily). If the monophasic cycle is due to changes in the hypophysis and the ovaries, the following treatment should be attempted: (1) Progesterone, 100 mg., i.m. administered from the 14th day of the cycle. (2) Oestrogene, i. v. injection of 20 mg. of natural, conjugated, equine oestrogene in a single dose on the 14th day of the cycle. Its positive effect manifests itself by ovulation within 24 hr. and the development of menstruation 2 weeks later. Coitus should take place 6 to 12 hr. after the i. v. injection. (3) Cyclic treatment. Oestrogene, 1.25 mg. twice daily for 3 weeks, or ethinyloestradiol, 0.05 mg. twice daily for 3 weeks, followed by progesterone, 100 mg. in an oily solution, in a single dose. (4) Gonadotrophin. This is the treatment of choice in hypophysial insufficiencies. It should be administered in a dose of 500 U. 3 times weekly, for 3 weeks. The stimulation of the ovaries is characterized by an increase in the size of the breasts, in the trophism of the vaginal smear, and by menstruation following administration of 100 mg of progesterone after the course of gonadotrophins. (5) Surgical treatment, in Stein-Leventhal's syndrome. The resection should be wide and bilateral. (6) Stimulating radiology. According to some authors, this method is indicated, whereas others reject it.
