N2  - This syndrome (named from the initial letters of its component parts in Spanish) requires surgical treatment, consisting of subperitoneal resection of the lumbo-ovarian blood vessel and nerve pedicle (Castano), wedge resection of the ovary and hysteropexy, with obliteration of the pouch of Douglas.
